Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.34,0:04:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不是那樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們突然配合的什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.47,0:04:36.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美容師遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:38.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可真喜歡玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  唯是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摔跤了嗎  一如既往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔  不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了不讓吉太被淋濕才變成這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.23,0:04:51.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.54,0:04:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裹上塑膠袋不就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.72,0:04:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得對啊  小澪真聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:04:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  一般都會想到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭髮雖然已經擦乾了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.34,0:05:05.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  變得好蓬亂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.29,0:05:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好不容易才梳好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.98,0:05:10.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅雨季節很潮濕  所以相當麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.13,0:05:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早上頭髮也是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是一到梅雨季節就每天早上在鏡子前奮鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.09,0:05:18.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  紬紬也是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:21.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以剛才很在意頭髮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.15,0:05:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是卷毛同志啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.66,0:05:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.24,0:05:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同是卷毛  但這差距算什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.59,0:05:35.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  不把衣服弄乾會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:37.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晾在活動室裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.64,0:05:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  讓你們陪著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔  室內鞋也都濕透了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.23,0:05:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊身褲也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.02,0:05:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我弄來了熱水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  一大早就喝茶？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.97,0:05:59.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用水桶來喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  是用來熱腳的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬紬  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.97,0:06:06.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就失禮了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.13,0:06:15.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服至極  舒服至極
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.69,0:06:19.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  已經不想上課了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.26,0:06:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.01,0:06:22.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  被訓斥了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.45,0:06:26.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  覺得暖和了之後就把衣服脫下來  要晾乾的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.81,0:06:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.61,0:06:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.15,0:06:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:41.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了  快點換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:49.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  我們已經把衣服掛起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.46,0:06:50.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.83,0:06:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.66,0:06:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被吉太看到這個樣子很難為情～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:06:57.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.72,0:06:59.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被敷衍了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.24,0:07:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  你要換什麼衣服？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.47,0:07:03.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天沒有體育課  所以沒帶運動服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:05.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.63,0:07:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有小佐和親手製作的衣服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.09,0:07:12.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕音社的負面遺產
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.65,0:07:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你選這件！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:22.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你把這個藏在哪兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.34,0:07:24.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明應該還給小佐和了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:26.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把這個留下了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:28.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  唯  果然在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:32.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點  班會要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:33.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:35.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會知道她是唯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.84,0:07:38.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？憑感覺就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.86,0:07:40.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊  和和
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:43.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能換的衣服只有這件嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.38,0:07:44.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也有別的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:48.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家早
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要點名了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.84,0:07:55.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平澤同學  你這是什麼打扮？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.04,0:07:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校服濕了  所以我就換上了這件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.03,0:08:02.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是  在學校裡打扮成這種奇怪的樣子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這衣服明明是小佐和做的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:08.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒別的衣服了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.77,0:08:09.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.41,0:08:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來遲了  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.49,0:08:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從其他班級的同學那裡借來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.11,0:08:20.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.41,0:08:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得的機會  想穿別的衣服看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.82,0:08:25.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了  快換掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓  找到忘拿的東西了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.87,0:08:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.31,0:08:35.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:36.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:42.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是姐姐的緊身褲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.45,0:08:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰啊  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.61,0:08:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把這些東西晾在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.45,0:08:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不出口…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:55.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,折縫燙不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.74,0:08:58.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.17,0:09:00.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:03.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎  拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.80,0:09:04.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬真熟練啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:06.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:07.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:08.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.79,0:09:10.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈕釦差點就要掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.22,0:09:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說你幫我縫好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.58,0:09:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.64,0:09:16.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.42,0:09:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.84,0:09:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不擅長這種精細活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.91,0:09:22.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,縫鈕釦倒是很快啊  律
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:23.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.84,0:09:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太浪費了  不想穿～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.27,0:09:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.11,0:09:31.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.01,0:09:33.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要坐下來就不會被發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.93,0:09:39.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問的是作為一個女生這樣可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律不也經常這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.42,0:09:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:44.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.32,0:09:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小佐和
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:49.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運動服要脫掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.29,0:09:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田井中同學也把下襟塞進去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.67,0:09:54.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:56.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前明明都不會生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:58.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天到底是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.02,0:10:02.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點  平澤同學  田井中同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.92,0:10:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.48,0:10:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.81,0:10:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:09.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也很不輕鬆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.24,0:10:11.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  您不用為我擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.08,0:10:14.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有為你擔心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平澤同學也快點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.82,0:10:19.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明這樣比較好的說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行就是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.31,0:10:24.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使裙子掀起來也沒事  摔跤了也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:25.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了  快點脫掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和  住手～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.70,0:10:32.42,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  被摸了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等  就像我在襲擊你似的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.53,0:10:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平澤同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.76,0:10:34.12,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:37.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是校服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.18,0:10:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點無聊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.67,0:10:40.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.98,0:10:43.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明大家都很期待的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:45.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用回應大家的期待也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.70,0:10:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  還在下雨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.99,0:10:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要被淋濕了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:52.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.27,0:10:53.72,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天好像也會下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.85,0:10:54.49,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:55.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去也要保護好吉太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.23,0:10:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-ON!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  早上還出了那種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.53,0:11:06.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.40,0:11:10.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我用了吉他的防水外套
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.06,0:11:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  還有那種東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:16.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在網上買的  還是很方便的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:18.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原價3000日元卻只要1980
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還送吉他用乾燥劑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這個也是在網上買的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.59,0:11:28.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  可以黏在牆上的吉他掛鉤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.24,0:11:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉墊的形狀哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:35.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這是讓手指張得更開的強化道具
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:38.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有別的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:42.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如在睡覺的時候培養節奏感的CD
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:44.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.30,0:11:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…這些全都有用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.98,0:11:49.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.55,0:11:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我終於知道在活動室晾衣服是怎麼回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:11:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為純她…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這說不定是什麼咒術
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.50,0:12:02.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨著誰  就對其下了詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.31,0:12:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.56,0:12:09.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你看  特地跑到音樂室來晾衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.31,0:12:11.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.28,0:12:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…講了那些話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:16.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憂沒好意思說吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  真是讓人刮目相看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.24,0:12:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然挺身去保護吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.60,0:12:24.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎嘿嘿  再誇幾句～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.29,0:12:27.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  要是不小心讓吉他見了水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:30.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指板上很容易發霉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.51,0:12:33.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿  這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:35.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開盒子就看到上面全是霉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.20,0:12:41.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道吉太已經面目全非…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.94,0:12:43.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒發霉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:46.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但琴弦有些生銹了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:48.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是該換弦了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.16,0:12:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次是什麼時候換的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:52.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個月前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還是換一下好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.49,0:12:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有新弦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.20,0:12:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.90,0:13:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:09.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉太！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.66,0:13:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然敢攻擊我！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.58,0:13:21.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說  請鬆開弦鈕再剪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:22.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  也是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.27,0:13:26.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉太  我現在就給你換新弦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.19,0:13:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛惜它是好事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:32.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也不用成天這麼開心地跟它講話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.18,0:13:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:34.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.19,0:13:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵你吃醋啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.83,0:13:44.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三角關係啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連律學姐也！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:47.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Triangle Love
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:49.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種苦惱的歌詞也不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連澪學姐也這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:54.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早點告訴我就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.17,0:13:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.78,0:13:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦終於換好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就燃盡了可怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.38,0:14:04.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  趕緊練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.46,0:14:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨也停了  感覺也好起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:06.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.04,0:14:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！趁現在趕緊回家吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.27,0:14:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不練習了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.63,0:14:12.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉太會淋濕的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又滿嘴吉太吉太的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.13,0:14:18.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵對我也是很重要的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:25.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚  濕乎乎的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:29.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前天姐姐吃剩下的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發霉了…！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.69,0:14:32.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶泡好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.58,0:14:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐發霉了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.34,0:14:40.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你難道吃了那個饅頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.61,0:14:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  沒啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.32,0:14:43.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你嘴邊上…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.12,0:14:46.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青海苔還沾著嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  中午吃過章魚丸子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.29,0:14:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅雨什麼時候是個頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:56.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨也不錯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:15:01.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一整天都可以這樣悠閒地在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.95,0:15:03.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.01,0:15:04.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.94,0:15:08.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始練吉他後  姐姐就一直都很滿足
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.36,0:15:17.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是會擔心能不能彈好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.84,0:15:23.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是太差勁的話  就覺得太對不起吉太了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.34,0:15:26.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但又說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.31,0:15:31.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能一直這麼快樂地在一起就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.15,0:15:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
