Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:26.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也下雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.02,0:16:28.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天沒問題！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.08,0:16:30.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏘～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.29,0:16:31.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這下放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太難拆了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.67,0:16:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包過頭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.72,0:16:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於拆完了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.21,0:16:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本的氣候對樂器比較苛刻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.89,0:16:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.96,0:16:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴頸受潮的話會彎曲導致走音的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.54,0:16:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試下八度調音就能聽出來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.71,0:16:57.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著  像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.70,0:17:04.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  我也試試
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.64,0:17:05.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.12,0:17:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:10.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏了半音的一半的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:10.97,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（半音：十二平均律相鄰的兩個音之間最小的距離叫半音，兩個半音距離構成一個全音）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.10,0:17:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.69,0:17:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用調諧器就能聽出來？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.86,0:17:14.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.02,0:17:20.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  和唯學姐說得一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:22.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏了1/8音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.87,0:17:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我調好吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己去調啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.12,0:17:28.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的話太花時間啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:31.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我不是都教過你了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.63,0:17:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下不為例哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:36.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  梓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.68,0:17:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨還是不見停啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.31,0:17:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.80,0:17:45.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風也越刮越大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:49.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣預報說明天還要繼續下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.89,0:17:52.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就把貝司放在活動室好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.87,0:17:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了！小澪！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.87,0:18:01.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.01,0:18:05.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可憐了  伊麗莎白！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:07.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要被拋棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.86,0:18:10.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不想淋濕才放在這裡的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.45,0:18:11.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有別隨便起名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.27,0:18:13.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不唯你的吉他也放活動室吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包裝用的塑膠紙…都成那樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要跟不認識的人走掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:28.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.90,0:18:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊麗莎白  今晚要和吉太一起過夜哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:33.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了不要隨便起名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:36.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fsp30}　{\fsp1}Bass{\fsp140}　{\fsp1}Elizabeth{\r}\N因為是貝司所以起名叫伊麗莎白麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.71,0:18:40.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fsp100}　{\fsp1}Mustang{\r}\N那麼  我的叫野馬…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:43.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…穆炭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.86,0:18:45.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好配的名字哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.03,0:18:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要隨便猜人家在想什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.99,0:18:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓你已經說出口了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.58,0:18:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔哇  這雨下得超大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:57.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞋子裡都進水了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.66,0:18:59.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好把樂器放學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.94,0:19:05.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大家  明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.85,0:19:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.07,0:19:08.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.20,0:19:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.12,0:19:10.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉太  好擔心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:19.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不帶吉他到頭來還是會淋濕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.84,0:19:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說唯也很重視她的吉他嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.06,0:19:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重視的方向錯了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.70,0:19:30.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就放一天而已  太誇張啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.39,0:19:34.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  說那樣的話好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:35.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:37.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次碰壞貝司的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.66,0:19:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭著跑來找我的事情你都不記得啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.35,0:19:41.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.97,0:19:42.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪兒呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.96,0:19:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:56.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作業終於做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:19:59.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.47,0:20:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…小偷？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.13,0:20:14.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:20.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐！我聽到奇怪的聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.81,0:20:23.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.89,0:20:27.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憂…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.34,0:20:28.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:30.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憂…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:32.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你沒事吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.30,0:20:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我擔心留在學校的吉太  睡不著覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.61,0:20:38.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.37,0:20:46.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來  買回吉他後天天都在練習
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.45,0:20:50.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都和吉太在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.47,0:20:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受不了了！我去取回來！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.91,0:20:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐！這裡是三層！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.39,0:21:00.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面下著雨！你還穿著睡衣！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.29,0:21:05.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一天沒碰而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:07.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你笑得嘴都歪了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.43,0:21:10.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你很重視這把吉他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.10,0:21:11.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.21,0:21:13.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.01,0:21:16.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過班會的時候能不能收起來？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.48,0:21:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.09,0:21:19.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很在意！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.36,0:21:21.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～就一下下  沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.53,0:21:22.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.86,0:21:33.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.71,0:21:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯她那個樣子  害得我都擔心起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.43,0:21:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開盒子就看到上面全是霉～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.31,0:21:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.92,0:22:02.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊麗莎白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.20,0:23:41.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕  好可怕  好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.71,0:23:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪搔癢耙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.31,0:23:44.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別弄出奇怪的東西來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.99,0:23:46.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是兩人的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.12,0:23:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.19,0:23:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在那之後等待著她們的命運…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.30,0:23:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.20,0:23:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就開始第一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.74,0:23:55.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止聽到過的最可怕的事是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.08,0:23:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  你在問什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.73,0:23:58.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.81,0:24:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二可怕的事是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.85,0:24:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個下一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.79,0:24:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三可怕的事是什麼～？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.07,0:24:09.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚…我明明已經要忘記那件事了…


